  "text": "This choice will become important in Section 10 as it fixes a notion of Satake parameters relative to a distinguished splitting of the L-group L Sp 2r (see [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] , and the work of Weissman more generally). Set Θ 2r := Θ(Sp 2r , χ) to be the corresponding theta representation.",
